The paper proposes a method for assessing the capacity of distributed generation in active distribution networks, which involves optimization techniques and power flow modeling. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including systems and control (cs.SY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), emerging technologies (cs.ET), and software engineering (cs.SE).
